the four freedoms

00:01:09.140 --> 00:01:13.460
that President Franklin Delano
Roosevelt had articulated

00:01:13.460 --> 00:01:19.010
in his 1941 State of the
Union address to Congress.

00:01:19.010 --> 00:01:23.260
