very, very well known by everyone

00:01:23.260 --> 00:01:30.680 position:56%
at the time were, of course, freedom
of religion, freedom of speech,

00:01:30.680 --> 00:01:36.310
freedom from want and
freedom from fear.

00:01:36.310 --> 00:01:42.100
Franklin Delano Roosevelt then
appointed the first lady Eleanor

00:01:42.100 --> 00:01:45.890
to spearhead an effort
through the United Nations

00:01:45.890 --> 00:01:49.990
to develop a universal
declaration of human rights.

00:01:49.990 --> 00:01:52.290
