many countries, Lebanon, Canada,

00:02:06.320 --> 00:02:10.930
the UK, Chile of course,
the United States,

00:02:10.930 --> 00:02:14.320
China, the then Soviet Union.

00:02:14.320 --> 00:02:18.020
