striking to think about in terms

00:02:18.020 --> 00:02:23.260
of our discussions about human
rights today and then of course,

00:02:23.260 --> 00:02:27.660
our esteem colleagues and panelists
that we will hear from shortly,

00:02:27.660 --> 00:02:32.330
