drafters were not just lawyers

00:02:32.330 --> 00:02:33.990
and jurists.

00:02:33.990 --> 00:02:41.470 position:56%
Among the drafters were playwrights,
art collectors, of course,

00:02:41.470 --> 00:02:49.030
