01:22:54.780 --> 01:23:00.330
the entire record of every opinion
ever reached lay at the disposal

01:23:00.330 --> 01:23:04.620
of the Muslim masses, including
moderate Islamist movements,

01:23:04.620 --> 01:23:08.530
