01:23:18.070 --> 01:23:20.500
as if they were the going opinion.

01:23:20.500 --> 01:23:22.280
And this without the benefit

01:23:22.280 --> 01:23:27.570
of knowing the important
distinction between law and fact.

01:23:27.570 --> 01:23:30.350
What renders this even
more problematic, however,

01:23:30.350 --> 01:23:33.270
is the fact that this rich
and variated [inaudible]

01:23:33.270 --> 01:23:37.520
of Muslim juristic opinion
is extremely valuable

01:23:37.520 --> 01:23:41.400
in demonstrating both the
pluralistic nature of Islamic law

01:23:41.400 --> 01:23:45.640
and the degree of intellectual
boldness and sophistication

01:23:45.640 --> 01:23:49.820
that went into Muslim
