01:24:16.520 --> 01:24:20.190
Yet, I must admit that I
remain stymied by this problem,

01:24:20.190 --> 01:24:22.940
I'm not sure how to handle it.

01:24:22.940 --> 01:24:26.870
In the end, however, whatever
solution the Muslim community

01:24:26.870 --> 01:24:32.390 position:56%
